Notebooks

Spreadsheets-are-all-you-need Notebooks are what happens when a spreadsheet and a python notebook have an AI powered baby in browser land.

To get started,

  • Click the plus icon (lower right of your screen) to build out a workflow of data tables.
  • Click the export button (lower left of your screen) to save your workflow in a self contained runnable HTML file that works locally.

Visit One file, Infinite possibilities: Introducing Spreadsheets-are-all-you-need Notebooks to learn more.
